title: CAF Confederation Cup semifinals results & scorers (2nd leg) - Africa - Sports
text:
First leg matches in parenthesis.
 (All times GMT)
Saturday 3 October
Zamalek (Egypt) 3-0 Etoile du Sahel (Tunisia) 1-5
Scorers: Mahmoud Kahraba 11, 55pen, Abderrazak 69
Etoile du Sahel reach the final after beating Zamalek 5-4 on aggregate
Sunday 4 October
Ahly (Egypt) 3-4 Orlando Pirates (S. Africa) 0-1
Scorer(s): Evouna 42', 53', Gamal 90+2/ Erasmus 58', Gabuza 75', Matlaba 86', Rakale 90+5
Orlando Pirates reach the final after beating Ahly 5-3 on aggregate
